[CLIENT IMPLEMENTATION] Endpoint that our client must implement to respond the Resources request ```(GET /accounts/{accountId})```. **FamilyType**: ```Contas``` This endpoint will be used by the Receiver to get the resources offered by our customer. This endpoint must behave exactly as the specified on the  [Open Banking Brazil Oficial Documentation](https://openfinancebrasil.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/OF/pages/578584735/Informa+es+T+cnicas+-+DC+Contas+-+v2.4.1), except by the Authentication type, it must implement a mTLS The path can be parametrized by the client, it is just a suggestion, except by the fact that it must receive the ```DataConsentId``` and ```PactualId``` as a route or query parameter.
